        "comment": "Some snow fell on Saturday over a wide area. Distinct weak layers exist in the old snowpack. This applies especially on west, north and east facing slopes. The snowpack remains generally prone to triggering. <br/> At high altitude the wind slabs have increased in size additionally in the last two days. <br/> The snowpack will be moist at low and intermediate altitudes."
